race.comment: KUNDA (4) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from five starts. In the money last time at this track (29.79) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 1.3 lengths third. Has the ability and should feature. IT'S A GLAM (8) is better than last start when seventh (30.53) in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park over 520m. Has a strong record here including nine wins. Has ability and is one of the better chances. MY CUPCAKE (3) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (29.99) at Gosford in a Grade 5. Lines up from box 3 for the first time. Has a good record here including three wins. Ready to find winning form. OCCULENT (6) scored last time and can measure up again.
